Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.87,0:00:05.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The Kingdom of Fiore...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.24,0:00:09.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A neutral country of 17 million people.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.66,0:00:12.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It is a world of magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.85,0:00:15.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Magic is bought and sold there every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.95,0:00:18.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It is an integral part of people's lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.96,0:00:23.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And there are those who use magic as their occupation.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.65,0:00:27.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Those people are referred to as wizards.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.98,0:00:34.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The wizards belong to various guilds \Nand perform jobs on commission.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.49,0:00:38.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There are a large number of guilds within the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.01,0:00:43.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And in a certain city there lies a certain guild.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.03,0:00:49.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A guild from which various legends were once born... Or \Nrather, will continue to be born long into the future...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.86,0:00:51.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And its name is:
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.60,0:00:55.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fairy Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.39,0:00:57.59,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Fairy, where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.59,0:01:06.71,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll gather all the light, and shine down on your tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.81,0:01:16.13,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah! Can you hear this voice?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.13,0:01:21.05,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah! It's hoarse from yelling.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.05,0:01:25.37,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah! Until your heart can hear it...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.37,0:01:29.48,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah! Oh, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.90,0:01:34.56,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,The moon and sun high-five.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.40,0:01:39.18,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure you're not forgetting something?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.12,0:01:44.58,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,When you're not here to make me laugh,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.58,0:01:47.72,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,even what I'm looking for can't be found.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.72,0:01:51.88,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Snowing, be honest with yourself and smile,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.88,0:01:56.73,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,because when two people lay close, time overlaps.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.73,0:01:58.56,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Fairy, where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.56,0:02:07.65,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll gather all the light, and shine down on your tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.27,0:02:12.69,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.81,0:02:27.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Last time on Fairy Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.43,0:02:32.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew you'd come, you Fairy Tail flies!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.13,0:02:34.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you after, you fiend?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.87,0:02:36.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you plan to do with the lullaby?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.80,0:02:39.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Titania Erza?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.13,0:02:42.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Circle Sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.94,0:02:47.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.18,0:02:49.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The station is surrounded by wind...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.10,0:02:54.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You fools cannot escape from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.29,0:02:58.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oshibana station.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.56,0:03:02.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I said we don't know already... It's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.24,0:03:06.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way we could dispel the magic wind wall!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.74,0:03:08.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.21,0:03:10.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray? You're not with Natsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.97,0:03:12.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We split up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.36,0:03:14.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And never mind that now!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.28,0:03:17.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Eisenwald's real objective is the town down the line from here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.67,0:03:18.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.46,0:03:20.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the place where the old men\Nare having their regular meeting!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.98,0:03:24.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They plan on using the lullaby there!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.12,0:03:25.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's what you're planning?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.53,0:03:29.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But this station is surrounded by a magic wind wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.34,0:03:31.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I saw it earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.37,0:03:35.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be mincemeat if you try and force yourself out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.37,0:03:36.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm well aware of that...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.34,0:03:39.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza, your arm...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.10,0:03:40.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.65,0:03:46.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But while we're sitting here, Erigor gets ever \Ncloser to where the Guild Masters are.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.59,0:03:52.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yes... There should be someone \Nthey call "Kage" in Eisenwald.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.58,0:03:56.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He was the only one who was able to dispel Lullaby's seal.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.55,0:03:58.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Dispel?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.22,0:03:59.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a Dispeller?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.93,0:04:02.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then he could dispel the magic wind wall, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.46,0:04:05.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Search for Kage and capture him!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.97,0:04:06.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.82,0:04:12.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Karacka, how long are you going to hide yourself there?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.24,0:04:16.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.21,0:04:18.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They're after Kage.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.10,0:04:19.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.34,0:04:23.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, not me! I'm useless as backup in a fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.16,0:04:27.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I have a much simpler task for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.81,0:04:33.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Flame and Wind!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.75,0:04:41.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've completely lost sight of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.11,0:04:41.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.99,0:04:44.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, why don't we head back to where Erza is for now?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.93,0:04:48.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that reaction?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.31,0:04:50.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza told us to go after him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.62,0:04:51.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.51,0:04:55.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so brave, Lucy... You'd ignore an order from Erza?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.32,0:04:57.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When Erza orders something, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.42,0:05:00.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,After the things she'll do to you, Lucy, \NI'm not sure I could look at you...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.93,0:05:03.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She's going to do "things" to me?! {I think the awkwardness helps the humor}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.44,0:05:04.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, I get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.46,0:05:07.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep looking until I find him!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.24,0:05:09.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Your attitude sure changes easily, Lucy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.68,0:05:11.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough out of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.19,0:05:14.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And why is this cat even following me anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.37,0:05:22.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erigor, where are you hiding?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.88,0:05:25.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Next!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.27,0:05:29.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Has this guy never heard of a door?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.26,0:05:32.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.70,0:05:38.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I suppose there's no problem if I just leave him alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.29,0:05:42.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But I wouldn't be satisfied with that, would I?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.87,0:05:50.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for earlier, you motion-sickness fly!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.70,0:05:54.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You {\i1}again{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.65,0:05:56.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That looks good on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.41,0:05:57.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, baldy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.72,0:06:00.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not bald, and my name's not Hage! It's Kageyama!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.29,0:06:01.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That so?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.72,0:06:03.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.30,0:06:05.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I basically understand your magic now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.41,0:06:08.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You ingest flames to increase your destructive power.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.61,0:06:10.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's quite rare magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.89,0:06:15.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I really {\i1}really{\i0} want to slug you one right \Nnow, but it's not the time for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.89,0:06:17.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is Erigor?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.97,0:06:23.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Good question. Maybe I'll tell you if you beat me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.09,0:06:26.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Knuckle Shadow!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.63,0:06:31.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? You'll tell me after I hit you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.00,0:06:33.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then that's two birds with one stone!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.46,0:06:35.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm all fired up now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.35,0:06:40.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that vibration?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.24,0:06:44.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a slippery one. {nice one!}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.77,0:06:45.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.42,0:06:49.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't dodge my Orochi Shadow! {orochi has been featured in many video games, I think it can be left without note as a name here obvious from visual context}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.57,0:06:51.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll follow you into the depths of hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.51,0:06:55.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tear you apart!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.75,0:06:58.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wing Slash of the Fire Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.81,0:07:06.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You've got to be kidding me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.89,0:07:09.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He destroyed the Orochi Shadow with a single attack?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.43,0:07:11.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What destructive power...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.25,0:07:13.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe a wizard like this exists!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.48,0:07:18.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How'd you like another one of my "fly" punches, eh? {check me}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.25,0:07:21.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,H-He's a monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.68,0:07:26.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.09,0:07:27.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.87,0:07:33.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my, it seems I've gone and destroyed the place again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.06,0:07:34.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why does it always end up like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.30,0:07:39.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I feel better now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.02,0:07:41.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I win, Decoyama. {there's no easy way to add in the double meaning here...}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.05,0:07:42.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Kageyama, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.73,0:07:46.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Tell me where Erigor is, like you promised!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.13,0:07:51.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fool... Master Erigor is no longer in this station.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.35,0:07:52.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.30,0:07:53.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.61,0:07:56.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough! We need him!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.63,0:07:58.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice going, flamebrain! {have something better for "kusohono?"... I was going for pun on "lamebrain" if that's not obvious}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.78,0:07:59.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.77,0:08:03.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't do nothin' but I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.93,0:08:07.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Dispel the magic wind wall, and don't give us any trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.08,0:08:11.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She ain't kidding', man!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.65,0:08:13.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza's a {\i1}beast{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.39,0:08:14.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.60,0:08:15.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.25,0:08:17.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.51,0:08:25.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.48,0:08:28.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A simple task...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.38,0:08:31.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kage!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.60,0:08:34.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Dispose of Kage!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.78,0:08:37.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! There goes our only exit!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.72,0:08:41.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kage, stay with me! We need your power!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.64,0:08:43.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, man!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.33,0:08:46.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the only one who can dispel the magic wind wall!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.47,0:08:47.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't die!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.68,0:08:54.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't he... your ally?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.68,0:08:59.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't he an ally in the same guild as you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.60,0:09:04.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.05,0:09:08.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's what your guild is like?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.11,0:09:10.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kage, you've got to stay with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.90,0:09:13.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use, Erza, he's unconscious.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.03,0:09:14.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't let you die!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.82,0:09:16.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Dispel the wind wall!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.01,0:09:18.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! He can't use magic in that sort of condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.87,0:09:21.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We must force him to do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.21,0:09:22.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.74,0:09:24.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I interrupting something?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.54,0:09:25.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.23,0:09:29.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Clover Canyon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.48,0:09:32.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A deep gorge that stretches all the \Nway into the depths of the land.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.93,0:09:38.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no way to cross it other than this railway.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.28,0:09:46.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The town of Clover where the \NGuild Masters are assembled is near. {not all, just the local league}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.50,0:09:51.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And I've recovered most of the magic power \Nthat I used creating that magic wind wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.40,0:09:53.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's fly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.78,0:09:59.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You fools who took away our jobs and our rights... Just you wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.72,0:10:04.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The death god will purge you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.26,0:10:09.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So Erigor's objective was the regular meeting?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.50,0:10:10.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.63,0:10:15.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erigor blocked the only route to Clover, and is heading there by air.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.96,0:10:18.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be possible to catch up to him in a magic 4 wheeler,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.69,0:10:22.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,but if we don't do something about this magic \Nwind wall we can't leave the station!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.16,0:10:24.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.25,0:10:31.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If we try and escape to the outside, that's what happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.73,0:10:36.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kage, I'm begging you! Lend us your power!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.40,0:10:38.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.12,0:10:42.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tear this wall to shreds!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.96,0:10:47.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.75,0:10:51.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot. Force isn't going to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.67,0:10:53.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be bad if we don't hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.39,0:10:56.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you freeze it with your magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.10,0:10:58.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If I could do that, I would have done it already.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.59,0:11:02.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.89,0:11:06.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop that already! You're going to smash yourself to pieces!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.29,0:11:08.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.52,0:11:10.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I said, stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.53,0:11:11.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.90,0:11:16.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.44,0:11:20.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it! Spirits!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.98,0:11:25.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I was able to transport between places by going through \Nthe Spirit world at the Everlue mansion, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.05,0:11:28.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, a normal person would die if they did that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.60,0:11:30.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't breathe.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.24,0:11:34.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And anyway, the gate can only \Nopen where the Celestial wizard is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.04,0:11:35.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.37,0:11:39.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, if you wanted to pass \Nthrough the spirit world to escape,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.47,0:11:42.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,the least you'd need is a Celestial wizard outside the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.30,0:11:44.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You lost me there...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.57,0:11:45.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Just hurry up and do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.86,0:11:47.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.84,0:11:52.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And it's also a really big violation of the contract \Nfor a human to enter the Spirit World.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.75,0:11:55.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's sure a good thing that it was Everlue's \Nkey when it happened last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.89,0:11:57.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup. I don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.49,0:12:00.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everlue's... key?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.11,0:12:04.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy, I remembered!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.63,0:12:05.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Remembered what?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.32,0:12:08.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The thing I was talking about when we came here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.20,0:12:11.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean when you kept calling me weird?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.51,0:12:12.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.90,0:12:15.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Virgo's key!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.96,0:12:17.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't just go stealing things!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.98,0:12:21.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But Virgo herself said to give it to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.72,0:12:26.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh. We don't have time to waste on this pointless crap.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.01,0:12:27.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Virgo?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.18,0:12:29.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean that maid guerrilla? {This is Natsu. I don't think he'd be so nuanced. I think he actually meant "gorilla." But this is your translation, so I leave it to you.}{I think he means "guerrilla" as in paid body guard, not as in gorilla body type.}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.91,0:12:34.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She said that since Everlue was \Narrested, his contract was broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.27,0:12:40.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So she visited us and said she wanted \Nto contract with you, Lucy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.17,0:12:42.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so she showed up? {Yeah, your interpretation is fine.}{check me}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.09,0:12:45.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I should be happy, but this isn't really the time, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.43,0:12:47.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We've got to think of a way out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.83,0:12:48.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.94,0:12:49.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.95,0:12:52.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Little kitties should sit there quietly and meow!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.62,0:12:54.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She can be pretty scary sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.17,0:12:55.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She's way stronger than you'd think!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.94,0:13:00.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But, Virgo can dig holes in the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.24,0:13:03.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I was thinking we could escape from the magic \Nwind wall by digging underneath it...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.26,0:13:05.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.25,0:13:06.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.30,0:13:07.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.57,0:13:08.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.34,0:13:10.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Way to go, Happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.51,0:13:12.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you say something earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.64,0:13:14.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you were pinching me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.23,0:13:19.19,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Begging for Forgiveness
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.42,0:13:16.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry! So sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.53,0:13:19.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you a reward later, I will! Please allow me to!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.88,0:13:21.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, just give me the key!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.43,0:13:22.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Looking forward to that reward!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.09,0:13:32.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I am linked to the path to the world of Celestial Spirits!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.14,0:13:37.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now! O Spirit, answer my call and pass through the Gate!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.53,0:13:44.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gate of the Maiden, I open thee!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.51,0:13:45.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Virgo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.86,0:14:01.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You called, Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.94,0:14:05.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.26,0:14:13.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You called, Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.65,0:14:15.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.83,0:14:18.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Marco, you really slimmed down.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.92,0:14:20.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Virgo.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.20,0:14:22.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize for the trouble I caused you earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.47,0:14:24.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Slimmed down? More like a different person!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.49,0:14:25.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A different person?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.61,0:14:27.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... What's with that appearance?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.45,0:14:30.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I am a Celestial Spirit that is faithful to her master.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.72,0:14:34.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I perform my duties in the appearance my master wishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.73,0:14:38.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You seemed a lot more powerful and forceful before, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.11,0:14:38.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.16,0:14:40.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.16,0:14:41.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I shall return to this form.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.85,0:14:43.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why'd you have to go and say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.93,0:14:45.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I prefer the slim version!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.77,0:14:47.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.32,0:14:49.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, we don't have any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.21,0:14:51.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Can we postpone the contract until later?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.21,0:14:53.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood, Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.38,0:14:55.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop calling me Master already, would you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.41,0:14:56.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then shall I call you Queen?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.74,0:14:57.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Rejected!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.71,0:14:58.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, Princess?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.94,0:15:00.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm, that might be nice...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.52,0:15:01.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's her thing, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.98,0:15:02.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, hurry up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.18,0:15:05.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I will proceed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.21,0:15:08.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ooh, she's digging!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.12,0:15:09.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Good going, Lucy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.25,0:15:09.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch! {lit: "Hard!" but I can't think of how that's work in english}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.89,0:15:12.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay everyone, into that hole!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.40,0:15:17.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, Natsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.30,0:15:21.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Havin' him die after I fought with him'll \Nleave a bad taste in my mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.99,0:15:28.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And so...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.97,0:15:30.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're out!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.37,0:15:31.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry onward!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.73,0:15:33.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, what wind!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.83,0:15:34.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.82,0:15:36.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Your underwear can be seen!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.45,0:15:37.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How about worrying about yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.94,0:15:38.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa there...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.18,0:15:42.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.03,0:15:44.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll never be able to catch up now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.60,0:15:48.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We... win...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.30,0:15:54.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Natsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.30,0:15:57.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy's not here, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.76,0:16:00.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the town... {at least in the manga, Clover is pretty small}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.49,0:16:02.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Just you wait, you old geezers!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.47,0:16:09.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you like Happy's max speed?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.31,0:16:15.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.25,0:16:19.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't fly anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.49,0:16:22.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to you I was able to catch up to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.52,0:16:24.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Damn you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.48,0:16:30.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're from Fairy Tail. Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.64,0:16:36.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,To defeat you, you blowhard!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.83,0:16:43.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why? Why did you take me with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.61,0:16:45.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The city was deserted.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.63,0:16:48.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So we're gonna take you to a doctor in Clover.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.79,0:16:50.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You should be grateful.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.29,0:16:54.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No... I mean, why did you save me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.11,0:16:55.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm your enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.78,0:16:59.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.91,0:17:02.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You plan on using me as a \Nhuman bargaining chip with Erigor.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.87,0:17:05.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It will never work. He's as cold blooded as they come.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.65,0:17:08.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He wouldn't do a thing for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.33,0:17:10.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.49,0:17:12.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to die, just say the word.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.98,0:17:14.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Gray!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.45,0:17:18.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything doesn't have to be decided \Nby life and death, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.38,0:17:21.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Think about the future a little, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.75,0:17:23.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All of you lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.65,0:17:30.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.48,0:17:32.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about that, everything's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.35,0:17:33.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.58,0:17:35.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't shove your big ass in my face!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.34,0:17:39.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's sexual harassment! Gray, kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.30,0:17:43.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't make light of my words of wisdom!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.60,0:17:45.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My vision is getting cloudy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.88,0:17:49.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems I truly have used up too much magic power.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.22,0:17:52.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu, please stop Erigor!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.62,0:17:58.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's up to you until we get there!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.60,0:18:04.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring it! I'll incinerate that dangerous flute!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.33,0:18:07.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You broke out from the magic wind wall?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.25,0:18:10.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What pests you flies are.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.10,0:18:12.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me through. Begone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.19,0:18:18.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This ain't...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.71,0:18:28.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.29,0:18:31.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He jumps and punches with flames?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.21,0:18:34.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And such force! I'd never think \Na wizard could punch like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.82,0:18:35.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.85,0:18:38.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop flutterin' around up there, it ain't fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.38,0:18:39.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Get down here and fight like a man!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.69,0:18:43.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get cocky, fly!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.76,0:18:47.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Storm Bringer!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.40,0:18:50.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.06,0:18:57.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use, I don't have enough magic power.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.17,0:19:04.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph. Flames can't help him fly!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.71,0:19:07.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.16,0:19:08.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,C-Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.85,0:19:10.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This doesn't look good!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.71,0:19:12.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.93,0:19:19.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,P-Pops?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.52,0:19:23.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're useless, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.21,0:19:25.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Take a good look.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.89,0:19:26.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.81,0:19:28.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.44,0:19:30.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's called a Purple Flare.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.24,0:19:33.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It can do lots of things other than just burning stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.91,0:19:36.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But mine just burns everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.11,0:19:38.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You can change the properties of the fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.52,0:19:43.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you wish it from your heart, the fire \Nwill respond naturally to your will.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.61,0:19:47.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And if you do that then fire won't lose to water or wind...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.97,0:19:49.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.79,0:20:05.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.27,0:20:10.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That was close.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.21,0:20:13.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Change the properties of the fire, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.74,0:20:15.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I did it, Macao!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.01,0:20:17.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.93,0:20:20.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You must be cold being all naked like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.37,0:20:21.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How about I warm you up?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.92,0:20:24.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't see you wearing a parka, either! {this is a callbak in the Japanese, so why not use the same line here to make it more obvious?  Maybe a bit out of character}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.95,0:20:28.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll blow you away!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.05,0:20:30.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Roar of the Fire Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.48,0:20:41.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Storm Wall!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.93,0:20:46.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.64,0:20:49.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He just attacks at random!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.60,0:20:52.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is what a Fairy Tail wizard is like?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.83,0:20:59.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems I underestimated your power a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.06,0:21:02.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How about we get serious now?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.44,0:21:04.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Both of us...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.03,0:21:07.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gettin' fired up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.36,0:21:09.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Storm Mail!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.06,0:21:16.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I come!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.23,0:21:24.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.63,0:21:25.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That all you got?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.02,0:21:30.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! Now you've gone and wrapped \Nyourself in something annoying!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.22,0:21:33.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tear it to shreds!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.22,0:21:36.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Iron Fist of the Fire Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.57,0:21:43.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.56,0:21:46.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The flame disappeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.26,0:21:51.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,As I thought... Without wrapping yourself in those \Nflames, you don't have that destructive power.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.19,0:21:53.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like it's no longer effective.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.66,0:22:01.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The Storm Mail's winds constantly blow outward.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.39,0:22:03.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.04,0:22:06.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Flames can stand up to a headwind!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.29,0:22:08.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Say what?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.68,0:22:14.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Flames can never defeat wind!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.81,0:22:28.61,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Take me away to someplace!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.61,0:22:33.61,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's ride on a tin horse, just the two of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.61,0:22:36.47,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,(Go!Go! Let's go! Romance)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.47,0:22:44.06,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,It's sad that my beloved doll can't talk to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.06,0:22:46.43,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,(Go!Go! Let's go! Romance)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.43,0:22:51.69,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Every time I think of you tears start to flow...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.69,0:22:56.81,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a crybaby, aren't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.81,0:22:59.46,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,In the moon (the moon) at night (at night)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.46,0:23:01.20,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm always (I'm always)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.20,0:23:04.50,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,searching for the rabbit!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.50,0:23:07.18,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm at a loss for words (Hey! Hey! Hey!)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.18,0:23:09.73,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,so much it's like I'm under a spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.73,0:23:12.97,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,This love is a monologue
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.97,0:23:15.11,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,from which I'll never awaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.11,0:23:17.62,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm at a loss for words (Hey! Hey! Hey!)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.62,0:23:20.34,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,since I've completely fallen in love.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.34,0:23:23.42,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what spell I could chant,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.42,0:23:25.56,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,to get through to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.56,0:23:29.51,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,The perfect thing to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.86,0:23:33.49,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Spouting this and that,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.49,0:23:36.10,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I just love you like crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.10,0:23:39.28,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,One day I want to be able to tell you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.28,0:23:41.55,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,"You got me."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.55,0:23:45.07,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,My words of thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.05,0:23:54.37,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing more to say!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.69,0:23:58.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza, Natsu, Gray, and me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.89,0:24:01.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think we balance each other out nicely?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.35,0:24:05.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,True. Feels to me like the best team in all of Fairy Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.93,0:24:07.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I know! Don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.91,0:24:12.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now we'll just do a bunch of jobs, \Nand I'll be famous in no time!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.38,0:24:15.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: The Strongest Team!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.75,0:24:20.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then the only question is how many cities \Nthis team will destroy... 2, maybe 3?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.06,0:24:22.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe 4 or 5?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.81,0:24:24.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me a break here!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.48,0:24:26.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,
